{"tid":712475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拒做樓奴　澳洲夫婦花23萬用沙包砌屋","createTime":"2018-06-22T06:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T06:59:33.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cc4165dbd39cc7022334e4d88b256a0bdfaa1117","tid":712475,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180622/_2018062213151460079.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180622%2F_2018062213151460079.jpg&h=3744bd69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">澳洲一對夫妻想擁有自己的房子，卻不想被成為「樓奴」，決定循不同方式動手打造家園。（網圖）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n澳洲西澳省一對夫妻想擁有自己的屋，卻不想做「樓奴」被房貸給制約，決定以自己的方式動手打造家園。於是他們買下一幅地，並利用一種特別的建築材料泥沙包（Earth bag），以新技術建造一座圓頂式建築，預計只需要花4萬澳元（約23萬港元），預計10年便可以還清。<br />\n<br />\n據澳洲廣播公司（ABC）報導，凱特（Kate Ryan-Taylor）和賴恩泰勒（Scott Ryan-Taylor）起初是因為不想花太多錢置業，才想出了這個方法。賴恩泰勒表示：「我們不想要背負房貸，直到我們七老八十。」於是向銀行借錢買下大約11公頃土地，然後向政府部門申請用泥沙包建屋。<br />\n<br />\n賴恩泰勒說：「我們想要的是我們有能力負擔的房子。我們不想等到已經退休，然後卻沒時間可以好好享受這個空間。」<br />\n<br />\n泥沙包能夠當建材鮮為人知，因為價格低廉、友善環境，被當成另類生活風格人士偏好的建材。泥沙包內有沙子、黏土、碎石，可將磚頭一樣排列造牆，並蓋成圓頂型建築。<br />\n<br />\n賴恩泰勒夫婦開始研究符合澳洲的建屋標準，包括節能、防止山火等，又要找工程師簽署地基和結構文件，也要找測量師進行相關手續，花了兩年時間，最終才獲准動工。賴恩泰勒說：「我們幾乎要向每名政府人員解釋泥沙包功能。」<br />\n<br />\n凱特和賴恩泰勒邀請了澳洲各地義工，協助他們在11公頃的自有地上建造這棟「泥土城堡」，這些義工同時可學到相關建造技巧。夫妻倆預計，建築費用會低於4萬澳元（約23萬港元）。「義工雖然要付出時間與汗水，但他們可以學習應付政府的繁文縟節，也可以學習如何興建泥沙包屋。」凱特表示。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180622/_2018062213151513845.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180622%2F_2018062213151513845.jpg&h=7a5d821c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">泥沙包中包含沙子、黏土、碎石，可將磚頭一樣排列造牆，並蓋成圓頂型建築。（網圖）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180622/_2018062213151665383.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180622%2F_2018062213151665383.jpg&h=8301cc7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">落手落腳自己用沙包砌屋。（網圖）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180622/_2018062213151659156.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180622%2F_2018062213151659156.jpg&h=43dfb543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">泥沙包能夠當建材鮮為人知。（網圖）</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/747424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F747424&d=FvZG0cN0CA52FazMClOsuJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=b7077432\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F747424&h=3b00372d\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/747424</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eabbe3fc4c5ed83bbfb892015b467468a006764","tid":712475,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:22:54.000Z","msg":"香港人A: 免費幫我起屋, 你可以學習應付政府的繁文縟節，也可以學習如何興建泥沙包屋<br />\n<br />\n香港人BCDE: 你都on lun9"},{"pid":"8685564a0d162a28d27bdc09f14ec7355ab027fc","tid":712475,"uid":92611,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"落雨點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1366c0260628e9c7bd7435547fa02f56c277db47","tid":712475,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:27:52.000Z","msg":"有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cd060da946f961f61efbbdd16e07eb5e20c840","tid":712475,"uid":27251,"lik